# Assignment Solutions

This document provides comprehensive documentation regarding the organization, storage, and navigation of all solution files within the Java Core Master Class repository.

---

## Overview

All assignment solution files for this Java learning repository are stored within the **`assignment/`** directory. This centralized location provides students with easy access to verified solutions for programming tasks and assignments throughout the course.

---

## Solution Storage Location

```
Java-Core-Master-Class
├── assignment/
│   └── solution.md          ← Solution files stored here
├── README.md
├── day01/
├── resources/
└── LICENSE
```

### Primary Solution Directory:

The **`assignment/`** folder serves as the designated location for all solution files. This includes:

- Completed assignment solutions
- Reference implementations
- Code examples demonstrating best practices
- Verified working code for tasks and exercises

---

