## Summary

All solution files for this Java Core Master Class repository are centralized in the **`assignment/`** directory. This organization provides a clear, accessible location for students to:

- Locate verified solutions to assignment problems
- Cross-reference their work with expert implementations
- Understand proper coding practices and patterns
- Progress through the learning curriculum effectively

For the complete folder structure, naming conventions, and detailed learning path, please refer to the main [`README.md`](../README.md) file.

